title: 207. nEw YeAr nEw mE
itunes:title: 207. nEw YeAr nEw mE
description: If you are waiting for the New Year to start working towards your goals, there's a high probability you will be disappointed. In today's episode, Andy talks about which mentality you must adopt heading into the New Year, why most people will spend their lives mediocre year after year, and the perfect time to start working towards your goals to build the life of your dreams.
